race.comment: TRAVOLTA (6) has the benefit of the one run back after closing late with a tidy fourth over 1600m at Randwick with the 59kg. Should come to hand quickly and looks set for a big campaign. PIGGYBACK (14) good staying mare who won the Colin Stephen with plenty in hand last prep. Resumed off the one trial with a solid fifth over 1600m at Randwick. Gets a better setup today from the draw and has genuine claims. SAM HAWKENS (15) imported gelding resuming. Disappointed at his first Australian start with a fading seventh in the G3 St Leger over 2600m at Randwick last October. Impressed in both trials and capable of taking this out. SIBAAQ (12) returns from a let-up after holding his form north of the border. Can roll forward and give cheek.
